sentences.english: The area that Miaka pointed to was the region where the constellations of Cancer and Gemini shone.
sentences.chinese: 美朱指着的那片天空正是双子星座和巨蟹星座。

sentences.english: Dozens of flights to and from the Twin Cities have been canceled.
sentences.chinese: 双子城的几十次往返航班都被取消。

sentences.english: The terrorists' attack completely destroyed the twin towers in New York.
sentences.chinese: 恐怖分子的袭击彻底摧毁了纽约的双子塔。

sentences.english: To you, Gemini's are irresponsible and unworthy of your dedication.
sentences.chinese: 双子座人通常缺乏责任心，并不值得你付出一切。

sentences.english: Gemini grabs both turkey wings for themselves.
sentences.chinese: 双子座独霸了两个鸡翅。

sentences.english: Libra is an air sign, like Gemini and Aquarius.
sentences.chinese: 天秤座和双子，水瓶一样，是一个风象星座。

sentences.english: You will make long strides in your career this year - as long as you keep faith in yourself.
sentences.chinese: 只要相信自己双子就会在职业生涯中会迈出一大步。

sentences.english: This eclipse falls on a fixed star Alhena, and that indicates some difficulty in travel.
sentences.chinese: 月食落入双子座意味着旅行中遭遇的困难。

sentences.english: The architectural appearance of focus plaza is a high 70 meters′Grand double sub-tower.
sentences.chinese: 福地广场为70米高的双子塔建筑外形，恢宏大气。

sentences.english: Central Business District(CBD) of Beijing, view from LG Twin Tower(East).
sentences.chinese: 从双子座大厦上拍摄北京中央商务区的一部分。

sentences.english: Aldrin had flown on the last of the Gemini flights.
sentences.chinese: 奥尔德林曾完成过“双子座”的最后一次太空飞行。

sentences.english: Gemini is a social creature, Scorpio likes privacy.
sentences.chinese: 双子是社交性的，而天蝎喜欢隐私。

sentences.english: The reticulate pattern of minor veins is characteristic of most dicotyledonous plants.
sentences.chinese: 细脉的网状式样是双子叶植物的主要特征。

sentences.english: After the twin towers collapsed , fashion week was cancelled.
sentences.chinese: 双子塔遭受了恐怖袭击后，时装周被取消了。

sentences.english: Ginseng is a perennial dicotyledonous herbs Nightshade classes.
sentences.chinese: 人参果属茄科类多年生双子叶草本植物。

sentences.english: The dicotyledons diverged at an early stage of their evolution into two main groups.
sentences.chinese: 双子叶植物在演化的早期阶段就已分化为两大支派。
